      <arrangement id="aspace_bc29d3b094fb843e5f43c5afdd745e32">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Organized into three series: I. Glass Plate Negatives, 1928-1931. II. Photographic Prints and Film Negatives, circa 1940s-1980s. III. Computer Media, circa 1976-1982.</p>
      </arrangement>
      <prefercite id="aspace_904f5ec238beabfaa3522b6695ca0d25">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
